German Budget Deficit May Fall Below 2.5% This Year, Bild Says

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-05-07T11:16:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-07/german-budget-deficit-may-fall-below-2-5-this-year-bild-says.html
Germany ’s budget deficit may fall
below 2.5 percent of the country’s gross domestic product this
year because of strong economic growth and rising revenue,  Bild 
reported today, citing unidentified people close to the federal
government.  To contact the reporter on this story:
